cat << EOF
pyliblo is a Python wrapper for the liblo OSC library. It supports almost the complete
functionality of liblo, allowing you to send and receive OSC messages using a nice and
simple Python API. 

Also included are the utilities send_osc and dump_osc. 
EOF
